---
title: Curried Cauliflower Cheese Filo Pie with Baby Leaf Salad
description: A twist on a puff pastry or mash topped pie, using scrunches of filo pastry to crown the creamy filling results in a golden and crispy top. Here, we're making a riff on cauliflower cheese by giving a mild curried flavour for a warming autumn supper.
